song_name: A Chase Isnt A Chase If Youre Not Running

version_description: This is easier and in my opinion the only correct version of this song on the website, chords wise. Enjoy my tab and rate:).
I've seen him play and I've watched him play this through a live video. I've run this through an experienced guitarist they agree with the chords.
This tab is based off the acoustic version (https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4gUbRR4GKzk).

This is basically just an acoustic version. It sounds good to me so if it helps you guys out give us suggestions. Basically, you when the drum bit is playing before the chords, mute all the strings and strum until the next chord comes up (Am) cheers guys and I hope it helps for now (Also some lyrics are probably wrong) x.
